<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="anyhow-adv">anyhow <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'enihaʊ/    美 /'enihaʊ/  </p>
<p>[句子副词]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-anyway">1.★ <strong>[非正式用语]不管怎样； 无论如何 (anyway)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It may rain, but anyhow I shall go out.
可能要下雨，但无论如何我都要出门。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There's nothing to eat. Anyhow, I'm not really hungry.
没有吃的了。反正我也不饿。</p></div></div>